headline: TikTok Ban Deadline Near. Trump Eyes 'TikTok America' Plan While Amazon Also Bids: Reports
summary: With a deadline for the TikTok ban days away, President Donald Trump was reportedly briefed on a framework to bring in new U.S. investors to keep the popular short-video app running.  Tech giant Amazon also has reportedly made a late push for the social media app.  The White House was close to approving a plan that would allow a group of investors to buy a stake in TikTok's U.S. operations, the Financial Times reported Wednesday, citing unnamed sources.
